DESCRIPTION:A support group for those with a diagnosis of prostate cancer\, whether recently diagnosed and wondering what happens next or those further through their cancer journey. \n\n\n\nThe group is LGBTQ+ inclusive and anyone with a diagnosis of prostate cancer is welcome to attend. \n\n\n\nFor more information or to register your interest\, please contact Dave. You can also visit the website.
