UID:10039365-1773307800-1773333000@tlchub.org.uk
SUMMARY:First Aid at Work Blended or Requal (3 day or 2 day)
DESCRIPTION:The course is suitable for people who work in high risk workplaces and covers the worst case scenarios and some of the more common minor stuff and goes on to cover common injuries and conditions a first aider might come across. \n\n\n\n3 Days/Blended – 1 day online learning\, 2 days in the Splat classroom. \n\n\n\nThe 3 day /Blended course means that 6 hours of work must be completed online prior to starting of the 2 day course. Without this completed online element\, delegates will not be able to attend training and places cannot be refunded. (Registration for the online element will be sent separately when booking is complete) \n\n\n\n2 Days/Requalifier –  2 days in the Splat classroom. \n\n\n\nYou are eligible for the 2-day requalifier\, if you have a current ‘First Aid at Work’ certificate. \n\n\n\nFirst Aid Training at Splat is relaxed and enjoyable. We aim to help you learn and support you to get what you need from the day. There are some practical and some multiple-choice assessments but our job is to ensure you have everything you need to pass these easily. \n\n\n\nPlease note that First Aid can be quite physical\, you will need to be able to kneel on the floor to perform CPR and Recovery Position. Please wear comfortable clothing you can move around in\, and\, if possible\, please let us know ahead of time if there is anything we can do to help support you and your enjoyment of the day.
URL:https://tlchub.org.uk/event/first-aid-at-work-blended-or-requal-3-day-or-2-day/2026-03-12/
LOCATION:Todmorden Learning Centre and Community Hub\, Todmorden Learning Centre and Community Hub\, Burnley Rd\, Todmorden\, OL14 7BX\, United Kingdom
CATEGORIES:First Aid,Learning
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://usercontent.one/wp/tlchub.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Splat-Logo-large-1024x576-1.png
ORGANIZER;CN="SPLAT - Amy":MAILTO:amy@splattraining.co.uk
END:VEVENT
